OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBreastfeeding mum told to  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fleave Rhyl swimming pool   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A woman said she was left feeling      
OL,6, humiliated after she was ordered from a
OL,7, swimming pool for breastfeeding.       
OL,9,FSarah Lappin was attending a           
OL,10,Fparent-and-toddler swimming session at 
OL,11,Fthe pool in Rhyl, Denbighshire, when   
OL,12,Fshe began feeding five-month-old son   
OL,13,FKalel.                                 
OL,15,FBut a lifeguard asked the 31-year-old  
OL,16,Fto leave the pool if she wished to     
OL,17,Fcontinue, even though it is legal to   
OL,18,Fbreastfeed in public.                  
OL,20,FRhyl Leisure Centre bosses have        
OL,21,Fapologised for causing offence.        
